Package io.github.akjo03.util.net.requests

Class HttpRequest

java.lang.Object
io.github.akjo03.util.net.requests.HttpRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Buildable
public class HttpRequest extends Object implements Buildable
Represents an HTTP request. Used to return an HttpResponse of the request by using a HttpMethod.
